{"3520180": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "與美食少女戀愛吧", "steam_appid": 3520180, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/af9e2411a5f9a00dd9a3f26b56bfb982.avif?t=1776451317\" width=780 height=131 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角是一位懷才不遇的廚師，能夠烹調任何料理。某天，他的料理在夜幕降臨時竟接連變身為不同的少女，他的生活就此天翻地覆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/991ccf1eacca4b45c0d1d2144fa690e5.poster.avif?t=1776451317\" width=780 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/991ccf1eacca4b45c0d1d2144fa690e5.webm?t=1776451317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/991ccf1eacca4b45c0d1d2144fa690e5.mp4?t=1776451317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>可愛又溫馨的烹飪約會遊戲。透過趣味小遊戲製作各式料理，接著與可愛女孩共度難忘之夜。我們致力於透過獨特的視覺風格、舒緩的音樂以及適中的難度，營造出令人放鬆的舒適氛圍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/933cd670c0774f80caea6fac4605e875.avif?t=1776451317\" width=780 height=131 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色各具特色，滿足所有喜好。每位少女都擁有與象徵食物相契合的獨特性格，各自背負著不同的過往、心願與煩惱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/760014464966d2aa4b7953a8abef2970.avif?t=1776451317\" width=1040 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水餃: 白晝溫柔體貼，入夜熾熱如火。將甘美多汁的滋味留給「那個唯一」。她不容許輕率對待，卻願將自己全然交付給傾注靈魂之人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >壽司: 一位倔強而驕傲的女孩。要觸及她的柔情本性絕非易事，但值得一試。冷冽卻優雅，恰似壽司應有的模樣。慣於光鮮亮麗的生活，但或許她渴望著別樣滋味？​​​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/9453f741dddecf4c555965a473759f72.avif?t=1776451317\" width=1040 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冬蔭功: 一位超級火辣的女孩。或許這正是你當下生活中需要的火熱？關鍵問題在於：你能駕馭她嗎？還是她會反過來玩弄你？面對這般尤物，你得當心提防。我們擔心的不是她，而是你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >千層麵: 端莊堅強的女性，能在廚房和烤箱前堅守兩小時。豐盛的份量與層層疊疊的美味，足以填飽任何飢腸轆轆的肚子。此刻，她正等待著真正的男人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/d0487747f2a7deb5e063d13a38b8a5f0.avif?t=1776451317\" width=1040 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >布丁: 可愛又有點害羞的小傢伙。她習慣保持冷靜克制，以免被強烈情緒意外融化。對待她時請溫柔細心些。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >披薩: 喜歡被關注和大團體聚會，但如果你能獨自吃完一整張披薩，她也願意和你一對一相處。她什麼都懂一點，永遠知道該聊什麼，不過常常會添油加醋、編些故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/9f74716dc1d40800e914c52f6cef5bea.avif?t=1776451317\" width=1040 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>牛排: </strong>大膽、愛冒險、喜歡尋求刺激、活在當下。當然，為了她你得花掉半個月的工資，但為了這具「多汁的身體」，有什麼不能做的呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提拉米蘇: </strong>是在咖啡館或圖書館共度時光的最佳伴侶。不在乎別人的看法。她的胸圍大小剛好能填滿你的心。她不只是女孩，簡直是一顆糖果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/b37c872790ca9858e7712333e4d724f7.avif?t=1776451317\" width=1040 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>薯條: </strong>又壞又愛嫉妒到極點，但又極度迷人。適合那些喜歡「重口味」、不怕麻煩的人。她會用無人能及的方式去愛你，並且會確保沒有任何競爭對手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>女店员: </strong>一個在自己家店鋪工作的年輕女孩。也許這不是一間普通的店鋪，也許她也並非一個普通的女孩。在一個盛大的戀愛故事中進一步了解她吧。也許她就是能帶給你幸福的那個人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/57fc1ad80717f35953ec85063fb0420d.avif?t=1776451317\" width=780 height=131 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有女孩的約會皆有配音。讓她們溫柔的嗓音陪伴您共度美好時光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個角色都有不同的故事和專屬事件。解鎖所有女孩的約會後，即可開啟結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/91250615ebf67f139e11663a16c19ada.poster.avif?t=1776451317\" width=780 height=780 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/91250615ebf67f139e11663a16c19ada.webm?t=1776451317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/91250615ebf67f139e11663a16c19ada.mp4?t=1776451317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/25cbee54b46937976cae85d35cebff63.avif?t=1776451317\" width=780 height=131 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你只對故事和小遊戲感興趣，你可以開啟“全年齡模式”，該模式會刪除所有性愛場景，並包含一些視覺屏蔽功能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras/3742f7c128d64d8abbab2a18759e743a.avif?t=1776451317\" width=780 height=215 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520180/extras